.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-REMOTE-PCT-VARIANCE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-remote-pct-variance \- FEAT-2955 channel-remote-pct-variance
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-remote-pct-variance
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the variance of the remote balance percentage across all peer channels for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2955).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBremote_pct_variance\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
